ngl-datepicker-input([formControl]="ctrl", required, label="Select a date")
|
|
p.slds-m-top_xx-small
  span.slds-text-color_success(*ngIf="ctrl.valid") {{ ctrl.value }} is a great FREE choice!
  span.slds-text-color_error(*ngIf="!ctrl.valid")
    ng-container(*ngIf="ctrl.errors['required']") Please select a date.
    ng-container(*ngIf="ctrl.errors['noMatch']") Only <b>10th of January</b> is valid!
